I need --define option in CompileTask, I am making it.
However, when I specify debug option, constant is not replaced.

For the command line:

http://code.google.com/p/closure-compiler/source/browse/trunk/src/com/google/javascript/jscomp/CommandLineRunner.java?r=653

    level.setOptionsForCompilationLevel(options);
    if (flags.debug) {
      level.setDebugOptionsForCompilationLevel(options);
    }

But for ant task:

http://code.google.com/p/closure-compiler/source/browse/trunk/src/com/google/javascript/jscomp/ant/CompileTask.java?r=653

    if (this.debugOptions) {
      this.compilationLevel.setDebugOptionsForCompilationLevel(options);
    } else {
      this.compilationLevel.setOptionsForCompilationLevel(options);
    }

Is this difference intentional?
